      "text": "# 📜 Proverb of The 64-Lap Inferno"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "a0a0ce8d9616b065",
      "text": "> The needle that returns to the same point sixty-four times does not merely mend a tear; it anchors the fabric of reality to the intent of the tailor."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "8cfd00f256df4e9e",
      "text": "— inscribed on [[The 64-Lap Inferno]]  ·  *The Velocity Dragon Blade*"
